00:38:56.640 --> 00:38:57.440 align:middle line:10%
>> Hey.

00:38:57.440 --> 00:38:58.430 align:middle line:10%
>> What an honor.

00:38:58.430 --> 00:38:58.940 align:middle line:10%
Thank you.

00:38:58.940 --> 00:38:59.780 align:middle line:10%
>> Real good to see you.

00:38:59.780 --> 00:39:00.740 align:middle line:90%
>> I'll give you a little tour.

